Quick Setup
-----------------------
* Install App on SH (also supports SHC)
* Download and expand wonderware_addon.tgz to your Splunk Deployment Server OR directly to an Archestra Server's $SPLUNK_HOME/etc/apps directory.  The tar file can be downloaded from: https://github.com/arcus-data/wonderware-app/tree/main/addon/wonderware_addon.tgz
* Edit inputs.conf to change the index and execution interval.
* Once data is flowing, manually run the "Wonderware Hosts - Lookup Gen" and "Wonderware Components - Lookup Gen". Note these searches are scheduled to run once/day.

See http://www.ossintegrators.com/blog/splunking-wonderware-industrial-data/ for more information on how to setup this App.
